{"tid":423408,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【MPF算賬】十隻表現最好港股基金有無你份？冠軍係...","createTime":"2017-10-04T01:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T01:14:24.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fce8c825185d47a2b63b7dc3e1a7b3b823aeaea0","tid":423408,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:14:24.000Z","msg":"港股發力帶挈打工仔強積金（MPF）有所進賬，根據晨星（亞洲）統計，全港53隻MPF港股及恒指基金首三季平均錄28.78%升幅，當中以海通香港特區基金表現最好，首三季大賺36.53%，同時跑贏其他類別的所有基金表現，暫列全港強積金榜首。<br />\n<br />\n今年首三季恒指累升24.4%，頭十隻表現最好港股及及恒指基金，依次排序包括海通、宏利、信安的800系列、交銀香港、景順及永明，首三季回報均達30%以上。<br />\n<br />\n若比較上述基金的長線回報，海通近5年回報仍然跑贏其餘9隻基金，累計升幅高達66.65%，而且收費亦是10隻基金中最平。由於海通於2014年起豁免3年管理費，其港股基金的最新平均基金開支比率（FER）僅為0.67%，相當於每1,000元供款只收7元管理費，遠低於其他有基金經理操盤的港股基金。<br />\n<br />\n至於安聯香港基金則於同類別中包尾，首三季回報僅錄23.76%，跑輸恒指，並與美國萬通、信安明智及易富之選、友邦、中銀保誠及東亞，一同跌入十隻表現最差的港股及及恒指基金。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上述基金又以友邦的收費最高，其港股基金的最近平均基金開支比率高達1.99%，相當於每1,000元供款收21元管理費。雖然收費是海通的三倍，但友邦首三季回報只有25.39%，跑輸海通近10個百分點，而回報亦低於市場平均。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171003/large/1507039252_ae2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171003%2Flarge%2F1507039252_ae2c.jpg&h=743ad41a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171003/large/1507039253_dff6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171003%2Flarge%2F1507039253_dff6.jpg&h=01b4f706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171003/large/1507039254_a753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171003%2Flarge%2F1507039254_a753.jpg&h=5879c3bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57287919&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57287919%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171004&d=eXP4m7GrBESckn%2BuOuspJ%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=2f0c8422\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57287919%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171004&h=6d3cf0ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57287919&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171004</a>"}]}